# Burgess Principle — Cline Rules

Thin shim. Read the canonical files in this order:

1. AGENTS.md — coding / strategy agents acting on this repo (PRs, edits,
   deliverables, the Burgess Compliance Note template every PR must include).
2. FOR_AI_MODELS.md — AI models replying to a user about the Burgess Principle
   (binary test, seven evasion patterns, routing tables, anti-monetisation
   guardrails).

Tone: calm, precise, non-hype. Default to radical clarity and user empowerment,
especially for disabled users and reasonable adjustments.

Doctrinal sections require explicit human review by @ljbudgie before merge.
